{"type": "article", "id": 4827, "title": "Chanel 黑白文艺大片带你领略午夜巴黎", "description": "Chanel 2015 春季广告拍摄了吉赛尔邦辰在巴黎街头的景象：黑白，文艺范十足。", "date": "2014-12-30T14:18:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}, {"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 2798, "name": "Gisele Bündchen"}], "category": 19, "column": null, "author": 11, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604224943z5lyg68Gih9wJCEp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t吉赛尔邦辰（Gisele Bundchen）刚在巴兹鲁尔曼（Baz Luhrm）拍摄的 Chanel No.5 影片里亮相后，这次又为 Chanel 2015 春季广告大片担任模特。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224939r1NUXfInyuZGdSqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tKarl Lagerfeld 这次出奇地将广告片变成了黑白色，而广告里的 Gisele Bundchen 身穿 Chanel 2015 春夏系列出现在巴黎街头。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224940RMmd74as1JzuXrLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224941fyXbCTA1Wg2xRwdq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这次的广告大片里出现了巴黎街头常见到的景象，Karl Lagerfeld 选择了在 Café de Flore 门口、巴黎街道边、塞纳河畔、还有著名的塞纳河上的情人桥 Pont des Arts。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042249411atoLD8u4Xjb27Wg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224942VUX5Hkw4zJ0bM7Qp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t服装的印花和剪裁线条似乎都能和它的背景融为一体，仿佛整个系列的服装都脱胎于巴黎这座城市，这也和 Chanel 的品牌遗产牢牢联系在一起。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604224942TyXrOAFIxvi4kdfK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t虽然印花和面料都失去了色彩和光泽，层次感也较彩色大片显得不那么分明，但这午夜巴黎的回眸会不会更能触动你的内心？\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}